title: Female Left Profile, Leaf Pattern Adjacent
description: A female in left profile is on the right with the eye cast downward and thickly lashed; a straight, slightly upturned nose; a rounded chin; and hair waved, close to the face and covering the ear. A foliate design is sketched next to the neck on the left and sprouts upward. The whole is enclosed in a rounded-edge square shape.
name: Drawing
